  "response_text": "# Daily Wellness Routine\n\n## Morning (6-8am)\n- **Hydrate** - Drink 16oz water before coffee\n- **Move** - 10-20 min stretch, walk, or light exercise\n- **Nourish** - Eat a balanced breakfast with protein and fiber\n- **Mindset** - 5 min meditation or journaling\n\n## Midday (12-1pm)\n- **Lunch break** - Eat away from your desk if possible\n- **Step outside** - 10-15 min fresh air and sunlight\n- **Rehydrate** - Another glass of water\n\n## Afternoon (3-4pm)\n- **Move again** - Brief walk or desk stretches\n- **Snack mindfully** - Nuts, fruit, or yogurt\n- **Reset** - 2-3 min breathing exercise if stressed\n\n## Evening (6-9pm)\n- **Dinner** - Balanced meal 2-3 hours before bed\n- **Connect** - Time with family, friends, or hobbies\n- **Limit screens** - Stop heavy use 30-60 min before sleep\n- **Wind down** - Light reading, gentle stretching, or tea\n\n## Before Bed\n- **Reflect** - Note 3 things you're grateful for\n- **Prepare** - Lay out tomorrow's essentials\n- **Sleep** - Aim for 7-9 hours in a cool, dark room\n\n**Adjust timing to fit your schedule—consistency matters more than perfection.**",
